# Upload Testing with UploadThing Integration

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/v1
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Upload Store Icon
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/store-icon
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

< ./path/to/your/icon.png

### Upload Store Banner
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/store-banner
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

< ./path/to/your/banner.jpg

### Create Store with Uploaded Images
POST {{baseUrl}}/stores
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storeName": "My Awesome Store",
  "storeSlug": "my-awesome-store",
  "storeIcon": "https://utfs.io/f/your-icon-key-here",
  "storeBanner": "https://utfs.io/f/your-banner-key-here",
  "description": "This is my awesome store with uploaded images"
}

### Update Store with New Images
PUT {{baseUrl}}/stores/store-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Store Name",
  "iconUrl": "https://utfs.io/f/new-icon-key-here",
  "bannerUrl": "https://utfs.io/f/new-banner-key-here"
}

### Delete Uploaded File
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/upload/file/file-key-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}